- 我还是觉得他们会远走高飞 - 走着瞧
- I still think they'll be long gone. - We'll see.

485
00:41:55,820 --> 00:41:57,130
老大?
Guv?

486
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:59,170
是的
Yes.

487
00:41:59,980 --> 00:42:02,142
一辆黑色的出租车要从你们旁边经过
Black cab just about to pass you,

488
00:42:02,143 --> 00:42:04,050
有5个人在里面,我觉得就是他们
five people inside.I think it's them.

489
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:06,810
看好你的位置
Hold your positions.

490
00:42:16,100 --> 00:42:17,810
等我的信号
Wait for my signal.

491
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:28,570
所以我说这是个美好的夜晚
That is what I call a great night.

492
00:42:28,660 --> 00:42:31,290
我不知道你们还要干吗 但我这个老家伙可要睡觉了
I don't know about the rest of you,the old man's gonna hit the sack.

493
00:42:31,380 --> 00:42:32,730
- 是啊,我想我还是跟你一起吧 - 真的吗?
- Yeah,I think I'll join you. - Really?

494
00:42:32,820 --> 00:42:35,530
不,我不是说要和你一起睡 我要睡我自己的床
No.I don't mean I'm gonna join you.I'm gonna have me own bed.

495
00:42:35,620 --> 00:42:37,770
- 我以为你不介意呢 - 我介意,我爱你,Albert
- I had no idea you cared. - I do care,I love you,Albert.

496
00:42:37,860 --> 00:42:40,420
- 你说你爱我.哦,我的上帝! - 闭嘴
- You said you loved me.Oh,my God! - Shut up.

497
00:42:40,500 --> 00:42:43,410
听着,你们各回各家吧 我可要去喝一杯
Listen,you lot do what you want,all right,'cause I'm gonna get a drink.

498
00:42:43,500 --> 00:42:46,210
我这两天可实在太受伤了
'Cause I've had a very traumatic couple of days.

499
00:42:46,820 --> 00:42:48,570
哦,拜托,我跟你一起
Come on,then,I'll keep you company.

500
00:42:52,380 --> 00:42:53,890
注意,注意
Eye,eye.

501
00:42:55,900 --> 00:42:57,690
站住.不许动
Stand still.Don't move.

502
00:43:01,020 --> 00:43:03,650
- 怎么了? - 你们被捕了
- What's going on? - You're all under arrest.

503
00:43:04,820 --> 00:43:06,210
为了什么?
For what?

504
00:43:09,180 --> 00:43:11,210
涉嫌偷窃
Suspicion of theft.

505
00:43:12,980 --> 00:43:16,850
对不起.我不明白你在说什么
I'm sorry,I have no idea what you're talking about.

506
00:43:18,380 --> 00:43:19,770
把他们带走
Take them away.

507
00:43:20,740 --> 00:43:21,720
这里,请,先生
This way,please,sir.

508
00:43:21,820 --> 00:43:24,380
...如果审讯的时候没有老实回答...
...it may harm your defense if you do not mention when questioned...

509
00:43:24,460 --> 00:43:26,290
你可以继续在法庭上申述
something that you later rely on in court.

510
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:28,650
但你所说的一切都会作为陈堂证供
Anything you do say may be given in evidence.

511
00:43:28,740 --> 00:43:31,730
我是警察局长的朋友 如果你打电话给他的话
I'm a friend of the police commissioner.If you'd just call him.

512
00:43:41,940 --> 00:43:44,370
一目了然,Mickey,派对结束了
Bang to rights,Mickey,party's over.

513
00:43:48,820 --> 00:43:49,930
排好队等着
Wait in line.

514
00:43:52,180 --> 00:43:53,650
我要跟我的辩护律师说话
I want to speak to my brief.

515
00:43:53,740 --> 00:43:55,770
会有时间的.就站在那里
In good time,just stand there.

516
00:43:58,700 --> 00:44:00,530
好了,谁先来?
All right,who's first?

517
00:44:06,340 --> 00:44:08,610
他以涉嫌发生在今晚
He's been arrested on suspicion of theft...

518
00:44:08,700 --> 00:44:11,450
10:30分在市政展览厅的偷窃罪名被捕
at the Guildhall Gallery at 10:30 this evening.

519
00:44:12,740 --> 00:44:14,610
- 姓名? - Ashley Morgan
- Name? - Ashley Morgan.

520
00:44:15,900 --> 00:44:18,490
- 生日? - 21/7/60.
- Date of birth? - 21/7/60.

521
00:44:18,940 --> 00:44:22,090
- 住址? - 列克星敦旅馆
- Address? - The Lexington Hotel.

522
00:44:22,620 --> 00:44:24,290
把你口袋中的东西拿出来,好吗?
Empty your pockets out,will you,please?

523
00:44:30,620 --> 00:44:32,010
你是不是忘了什么东西了?
You've forgotten something?

524
00:44:42,900 --> 00:44:44,650
- 把这个冲出来 - 长官
- Get this developed. - Sir.

525
00:44:44,940 --> 00:44:46,050
脱下你的领带
Take your tie off.

526
00:44:47,340 --> 00:44:48,530
第3个
Number three.

527
00:44:48,900 --> 00:44:52,210
没有在列克星敦旅馆那么舒服 但你也没有选择了
Not quite as comfortable as the Lexington,but you'll have to make do.

528
00:44:53,580 --> 00:44:54,800
好了,谁是下一个?
All right,who's next?

529
00:45:01,740 --> 00:45:03,770
警长刚刚证实...
Police chiefs have just confirmed...

530
00:45:03,860 --> 00:45:06,320
有5个嫌疑犯已经被拘捕...
that five suspects have been detained for the theft...

531
00:45:06,420 --> 00:45:10,690
罪名是盗窃世界著名的钻石,非洲之星
of one of the world's best known diamonds,the First Star of Africa.

532
00:45:10,940 --> 00:45:14,210
无价之宝,被镶嵌在国王权杖上...
The priceless diamond,which usually adorns the Royal Scepter...

533
00:45:14,300 --> 00:45:17,170
最近刚从伦敦塔运出,放置到...
was recently moved from the Tower of London,to be placed...

534
00:45:17,260 --> 00:45:21,370
市政展览馆作为特别公众展出的中心展品
as the centerpiece in a special public exhibition at the Guildhall Gallery.

535
00:45:31,740 --> 00:45:34,570
继续对Michael Stone的审讯
Resuming interview with Michael Stone.

536
00:45:35,940 --> 00:45:38,050
早上9:13
9:13 a.m.

537
00:45:38,420 --> 00:45:41,450
那么,Mickey,你已经有很多时间来思考了
So,Mickey,you've had a bit of time to think.

538
00:45:41,540 --> 00:45:44,530
- 是啊 - 你有什么要告诉我们的吗?
- Yeah. - Is there anything you'd like to tell us?

539
00:45:46,580 --> 00:45:49,850
- 无可奉告 - 那我会再问你一次
- Nothing springs to mind. - Then I will ask you again.

540
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:54,410
你能否告诉我昨天晚上 10:30的时候你在哪里?
Can you tell me again where you were at 10:30 last night?

541
00:45:54,940 --> 00:45:58,130
- 我不太记得了 - 还没有到12个小时呢
- It's slipped my mind. - It's less than 12 hours ago.

542
00:45:58,220 --> 00:46:00,210
是的,我知道.但我的记性不太好
Yeah,I know,I've got a terrible memory.

543
00:46:00,300 --> 00:46:02,170
10:30?
10:30?

544
00:46:04,100 --> 00:46:07,090
我记起来了.不,又忘记了
I remember.No,it's gone again.

545
00:46:07,180 --> 00:46:09,090
我真的很抱歉,但我的...
I'm terribly sorry,but my....

546
00:46:11,140 --> 00:46:15,930
怎么说来着?记性 我的记性实在不好,你也看见了
What's the word?Memory.It isn't quite what it was,you see.

547
00:46:17,020 --> 00:46:18,650
你在说什么?
What were you saying?

548
00:46:23,420 --> 00:46:24,480
有什么苦工的机会吗?
Any chance of a fag?

549
00:46:24,580 --> 00:46:28,650
抢劫?太可怕了 你抓住谁了吗?
A robbery?How thrilling.Have you caught anyone yet?

550
00:46:29,780 --> 00:46:31,090
谢谢你,亲爱的
Thank you,sweetheart.

551
00:46:34,780 --> 00:46:38,370
瞧,我真的不知道你在说什么,长官
Look,I really have no idea what you're talking about,Officer.

552
00:46:40,260 --> 00:46:44,170
审讯暂停,上午9:18分
Interview suspended,9:18 a.m.

553
00:46:49,700 --> 00:46:52,130
- 钻石在哪里,Mickey? - 可以这样吗?
- Where's the diamond,Mickey? - Is that allowed?

554
00:46:52,220 --> 00:46:54,450
那该死的钻石到底在哪里?
Where's the bloody diamond?

555
00:46:54,740 --> 00:46:55,800
什么?
What?

556
00:46:57,540 --> 00:46:59,170
我能说句话吗,老大?
Can I have a word,guv?

557
00:47:03,380 --> 00:47:07,330
你或许觉得你是清白的 但我知道就是你做的
You might think you're clever,but I know you did this.

558
00:47:08,340 --> 00:47:10,250
我会把你关起来
And I'm going to put you away.

559
00:47:11,340 --> 00:47:14,210
- 不管有没有钻石 - 长官?
- With or without the diamond. - Sir?

560
00:47:22,620 --> 00:47:24,450
我想你最好看看这个
I think you better see this.

561
00:47:30,500 --> 00:47:33,210
这是我们从Morgan的相机里得到的照片
It's the film we took from Morgan's camera.

562
00:47:44,380 --> 00:47:47,850
测试.1,2,3,4.你们后面的能听得到我吗?
Testing.One,two,three,four.Can you hear me at the back?

563
00:47:47,940 --> 00:47:50,690
女士们先生们,欢迎来到警局 英勇奖章颁发现场
Ladies and gentlemen,welcome to the Police Courage Awards.

564
00:47:50,780 --> 00:47:53,010
请大家按位子坐好
Would you please make your way towards your seats.

565
00:47:53,100 --> 00:47:56,090
典礼马上就开始.谢谢
And the ceremonies will begin very shortly.Thank you.

566
00:47:57,700 --> 00:48:01,850
今晚要颁发的是新近设立的 市民奖项
And now the last of tonight's civilian awards goes to a late entry.

567
00:48:01,940 --> 00:48:05,050
某人就在几天之前...
Someone who was brought to the Commissioner's attention...

568
00:48:05,140 --> 00:48:06,970
引起了委员的注意
only a few days ago.

569
00:48:10,300 --> 00:48:11,730
谢谢
Thank you.

570
00:48:12,980 --> 00:48:14,930
服务员,我要一份这个
Waiter,I'll have one of those.

571
00:48:20,460 --> 00:48:23,690
有一个人,不顾自身安危...
A man who,without any thought for his own safety...

572
00:48:23,780 --> 00:48:26,130
挽救了一名年轻路人的生命
saved the life of a fellow rambler.

573
00:48:26,620 --> 00:48:30,930
Michael Stone和那个他拯救了 的人,Daniel Blue
Michael Stone and the man who's life he saved,Daniel Blue.

574
00:48:39,380 --> 00:48:41,130
我正在河边慢跑
I was leaning down.

575
00:48:41,820 --> 00:48:45,770
看见了一只受伤的小鸭子
There was an injured duck,you see.

576
00:48:45,860 --> 00:48:49,250
我正试图帮助...
So there I was just trying to help...

577
00:48:49,820 --> 00:48:53,650
帮助这个可怜的小家伙 突然,我一失足...
just help the little fellow,when suddenly,I lost me footing...

578
00:48:53,740 --> 00:48:57,770
等我能意识到的时候 我已经在水里了
and the next thing I knew,I was in the water.

579
00:48:58,380 --> 00:49:00,890
- 为什么是我? - 你抽到了最短的麦杆
- Why me? - You drew the short straw.

580
00:49:01,700 --> 00:49:03,410
我要申述
I demand a recount.

581
00:49:07,780 --> 00:49:09,530
你推我下去的时候...
So when you gonna push me...

582
00:49:10,020 --> 00:49:12,580
我快淹死了.几乎淹死了
I was drowning.Definitely drowning.

583
00:49:12,900 --> 00:49:14,490
- 我不会游泳.救命 - 嘿
- I can't swim.Help. - Hey.

584
00:49:14,580 --> 00:49:18,450
我的一生在眼前像电影一般放过...
My whole life started flashing before me...

585
00:49:19,540 --> 00:49:20,890
我刚刚离开学校...
I'd just left school...

586
00:49:20,980 --> 00:49:25,090
然后就感到有一双坚强的手把 我拉了起来
and I felt a strong hand pulling me up.

587
00:49:26,100 --> 00:49:28,480
那就是他,那就是他
There he is,there he is.

588
00:49:29,580 --> 00:49:30,970
那就是Stone先生
It was Mr.Stone.

589
00:49:32,060 --> 00:49:34,090
他...
He...

590
00:49:35,900 --> 00:49:37,850
救了我的命.谢谢
saved my life.Thank you.

591
00:49:56,500 --> 00:49:57,560
没什么的
Doesn't mean anything.

592
00:49:57,660 --> 00:50:01,050
在没有钻石这种情况下 我们没法逮捕他们
We've got nothing to place them at the scene and no diamond.

593
00:50:01,620 --> 00:50:04,450
- 他们肯定藏起来了 - 那更糟糕
- They've hidden it. - It gets worse.

594
00:50:05,020 --> 00:50:08,450
我们知道钻石在10:30被偷的时候 离典礼地有半英里
We know the diamond was stolen half a mile from the ceremony at 10:30.

595
00:50:10,220 --> 00:50:11,890
看专员的手表
The Commissioner's watch.

596
00:50:24,940 --> 00:50:26,810
上面是10:20
It says 10:20.

597
00:51:14,780 --> 00:51:16,170
你忘了什么东西
You've forgotten something.

598
00:51:26,020 --> 00:51:27,370
那....
That's....

599
00:51:29,340 --> 00:51:31,170
那不可能
That's not possible.

600
00:51:34,860 --> 00:51:38,770
而后只要在最后,在上面洒上一层薄粉
And then just at the end,they add the little sprinkles on top.

601
00:51:40,180 --> 00:51:42,480
就做成了一杯摩卡咖啡
And that's what makes it a mochaccino.

602
00:51:45,340 --> 00:51:48,010
- 你可以走了 - 我没听清?
- You're free to go. - I'm sorry?

603
00:51:48,500 --> 00:51:50,530
我说,你可以走了
I said you're free to go.

604
00:51:51,340 --> 00:51:53,970
好吧,但我突然想起来了,我那个时候在...
Okay.It's just come back to me,where I was...

605
00:51:54,060 --> 00:51:55,570
把他弄出去
Get him out of here.

606
00:52:02,420 --> 00:52:04,720
很高兴又见到你.很有意思
Nice to see you again.It's been fun.

607
00:52:09,780 --> 00:52:13,050
事情还没有结束.你们还必须要转移钻石
It's not over yet.You still have to move the diamond.

608
00:52:14,140 --> 00:52:17,210
而你转移的时候,我就等在那里
And when you do,I'll be there.

609
00:52:31,940 --> 00:52:33,650
- 你都去哪里了? - 嘿
- Where have you been? - Hey.

610
00:52:34,300 --> 00:52:37,410
那个可爱的押管警官 他让我用了他的电话
The nice custody sergeant,he let me use his phone.

611
00:52:37,500 --> 00:52:38,930
拜托,我们还没搞定呢
Come on,we haven't got long.

612
00:53:02,100 --> 00:53:03,370
英国中央情报部
CID.

613
00:53:06,540 --> 00:53:07,680
你肯定?
Are you sure?

614
00:53:09,780 --> 00:53:11,130
好的,谢谢
Okay,thank you.

615
00:53:12,300 --> 00:53:13,770
长官
Sir.

616
00:53:14,820 --> 00:53:16,610
我们找到钻石了
We've found the diamond.

617
00:53:21,500 --> 00:53:22,810
太好了
Yes.

618
00:53:24,860 --> 00:53:27,850
- 在哪里? - 还在展览馆里
- Where is it? - It's still at the gallery.

619
00:53:29,900 --> 00:53:31,290
Doris,我们做得如何了?
Doris,how did we do?

620
00:53:32,900 --> 00:53:34,530
根据你的要求,复制了5份
Five copies as ordered.

621
00:53:38,220 --> 00:53:40,890
太好了,Lily,再来一张,谢谢
That's great,Lily,just one more,please.

622
00:53:41,900 --> 00:53:43,330
我不懂了
I don't understand.

623
00:53:44,940 --> 00:53:46,890
为什么惹了那么大的麻烦...
Why go to all this trouble...

624
00:53:48,100 --> 00:53:50,370
却不拿走钻石?
and not even take the diamond?

625
00:55:01,500 --> 00:55:05,250
英格兰政府一定对这次偷盗非常难堪
The British government are naturally very embarrassed by this theft.

626
00:55:05,620 --> 00:55:09,930
所以Ml6不得不编造出一个故事 来挽回他们的颜面
So Ml6 has come up with a plan to invent a story to save face.

627
00:55:10,980 --> 00:55:13,250
他们会说钻石已经找到了...
They'll say the diamond has been found...

628
00:55:13,340 --> 00:55:15,170
犯罪者也已经被抓住
and the perpetrators caught.

629
00:55:15,540 --> 00:55:19,730
然后他们会把一颗赝品放进权杖 并重新放入伦敦塔
They'll then put a replica into the Royal Scepter and replace it in the Tower.

630
00:55:20,260 --> 00:55:23,210
是啊,我们期待着掩盖故事...
Yeah,we're expecting the cover-up story to hit the press...

631
00:55:23,300 --> 00:55:26,010
就在今天晚些时候,你能看到的
some time later today,just so you know.

632
00:55:26,860 --> 00:55:31,130
然后,我所要做的就是来问你的出价了 我能用你的电话吗?
So then,all that leaves me to do is to ask you,can I use your phone?

633
00:55:31,580 --> 00:55:32,970
谢谢
Thank you.

634
00:55:38,380 --> 00:55:39,410
你好啊,妈妈?
Hello,Mom?

635
00:56:04,580 --> 00:56:05,970
警察吗?
Police?

636
00:56:06,540 --> 00:56:11,010
我想报告一些被盗物品的下落
I'd like to report the whereabouts of some stolen goods.

637
00:56:19,740 --> 00:56:21,890
- 你获得特赦了? - 正在着手处理
- You got your amnesty? - In writing.

638
00:56:22,580 --> 00:56:23,800
那么Benny...
And Benny...

639
00:56:25,260 --> 00:56:28,530
- 好好享受你的退休吧 - 我肯定会的
- enjoy your retirement. - I certainly will.

640
00:56:35,940 --> 00:56:37,810
哦,你这小信的人啊
Oh,ye of little faith.

641
00:56:39,260 --> 00:56:40,810
你瞧,这是场完美的骗局
You see,it's the perfect con.

642
00:56:40,900 --> 00:56:43,690
没有犯罪行为,所以没有人会为此被捕
There's no crime,so there's nothing to be arrested for.

643
00:56:43,780 --> 00:56:47,770
唯一的输家就是那5个贪婪的 猪头买了5个赝品钻石
And the only losers are five mugs greedy enough to buy five fake diamonds.

644
00:56:47,860 --> 00:56:50,050
当他们发现他们被骗的时候...
And when they find out they've been conned...

645
00:56:51,260 --> 00:56:52,370
又会向谁去说呢?
who are they gonna tell?

646
00:57:08,860 --> 00:57:11,490
这些,净赚的钱
There it is,back of the net.

647
00:57:11,780 --> 00:57:15,010
好吧,我们要先干一杯 为了Mickey Bricks干杯...
Right,this is a toast.A toast to Mickey Bricks...

648
00:57:15,100 --> 00:57:19,130
- 一个不容置疑的伟大天才 - 值得任何荣誉
- who is without doubt,a bleeding genius. - Worthy of any of the greats.

